#

Garlic Butter Steak Bites with Zucchini Noodles

20 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthyEasyHigh-Protein

Description

Juicy steak bites sautéed in garlic butter served over fresh zucchini noodles for a healthy, delicious meal.

Ingredients

  • steak (sirloin or ribeye): 1 pound
  • zucchini: 2 medium
  • garlic cloves: 4
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes (optional): 1/2 teaspoon
  • parsley (for garnish): a few sprigs
